Palʊla Jean de Dieu Madilu Bialu Makiese Wabulakombe kɛ [[agoza fenaɣ]] 28 wiye pɩnaɣ 1950 kɛ Kisantu ɖoŋgiye taa, Paa-koŋgo ɛgetiye taa [[Kɔŋgo Pirazaaviili|Koŋgo]] ɛjaɖɛ taa nɛ ɛsɩ [[Kɩyɛɛna fenaɣ|kɩyɛna fenaɣ]] taa kɩyakʊ 11wiye pɩnaɣ 2007 kɛ [[Kinsasa|Kɩnsasa]]. Ɛkɛna Koŋgo taa hendu teyu sɔsɔ nɔɔyʊ.

Palʊla-ɩ [[aloma fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 28 wiye pɩnaɣ 1950 kɛ Kisantu tɛtʊ taa kɛ Paa Koŋgo egeɣtiye, Kinsasa hɔɔlʊʊ taa RDC ɛjaɖɛ taa. Ɛ-hɩla kɩsɛsɛna ɖɔwa nɛ a-taa kɔyɔ: "Madilu System", "Madilu Multi System", "Grand Ninja" ou "Le Grand Pharaon". 

Ɛpaɣza hendu teu pɩnaɣ 1970 kɛ Bamboula taa. Puwayɩ yɔ ɛnɛ Yosha nɛ Pindu paɖʊ kɩgaʊ ŋgbɛyɛ naɖɩyɛ nɛ payaa-ɖɩ se Makuba Mayopi. Pɩnaɣ 1975 taa kɛ ɛkpaɣ lɩmaɣza se ɛtʊlɩ ɛmaɣmaɣ e-hendu teu pɩlɩʊ, Pamba Pamba.

Koŋgo ɛjaɖɛ taa hendu teyu sɔsɔ ɛnɛ ɛsɩba Kinsasa ɖakʊta nakʊyʊ taa mazaɣ nakayɩ wiye kɛ [[kɩyɛɛna fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 11 wiye pɩnaɣ 2007 kɛ tanandɛ ñɩɩtʊ lʊbɛ yɔɔ ɛɛwɛna pɩnzɩ 57. Ɛ-halʊ wɛ Muwasi-Gramayɛlɩ tɛtʊ taa, [[Fransɩɩ|Fransɩ]] ɛjaɖɛ taa.
